'''Addad''' (assaɣ nns amassnan: Atractylis gummifera) iga yan ummɣay iṭṭafn isnnann, gis yan ajjig amjahdi s uklu anibi, assaɣ nns "Addad" aẓaṛ nns zzɣ [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]] d ifta zzɣ gis s tutlayt [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛṛabt]]. Dars kigan n ibɣurn gisn mas ar itt ussmrs i tajjit n ukucm d uxamuc d tmuḍan n turin d kigan n tmuḍan yaḍnin slawann akkʷ tid gisnt ittuẓlan s uṣmmiḍ...

Ar nwwan iẓuṛan nns d ar ttussan mas ṛwan i yiwriɣ d ustci, d ar itt usmrs i tajjit n tmuḍan n ugullel d uhistirya, d a wer nttu mas ifulki i wgjjiḍ  d tkuli n udm d ula i tḥbba n tiɛεurma d tisɣi  ...

S usgzl ammɣay ad n waddad iga yan ummɣay iɣ ggutn ibɣurn .. macc ar ittɣama iga ucrim ur a yettudca.

